| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-0206 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: e5a7b0cf-e8d0-5256-8b93-64a9509f58c3"
